	abstract = {We give an overview of a domestic energy monitoring project which we are currently setting up in Brighton, UK, that will study the eﬀect that publicly displaying a household’s electricity consumption has on their energy usage. We describe our approach to designing: i) a low cost and low energy electricity monitoring system; and ii) eﬀective displays of domestic electricity use that indicate both current and longer term consumption and how this relates to the street average.},
